name: Tribute to Peurto Rico
description: The 11 year old artist who made this has a grandfather who was born and raised in Peurto Rico, a territory of the United States.  She is about to embark on her first journey to visit Peurto Rico and her extended family that lives there.  (artist has no twitter being 11 - Art mentor is Lily White @rblbab for contact/verification purposes)
